| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-2794 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e250636c-81bc-5023-bb44-936ed7910587"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
